{
  "texts": [
    "However, the number of studies on applying LLMs to enhance EFL learners' writing motivation is limited, and their effects remain debatable.",
    "For these studies with different conclusions, age and education level seem to be the main differences among their samples.",
    "College students seem to gain confidence from writing with LLMs more significantly, but secondary school students would be overwhelmed for undetermined reasons.",
    "Therefore, more studies to discover which factors increase these students' cognitive loads to develop more suitable LLMs are needed.",
    "DiscussionThe reviewed articles in this paper demonstrate the practicable methods of applying LLMs to EFL speaking and writing education."
  ]
}